
<div class="page-header">
    <ol class="breadcrumb">
        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/admin">Dashboard</a></li>
        <li class="breadcrumb-item active">OpenSubtitles Settings</li>
    </ol>
    <h1 class="page-title">OpenSubtitles API Settings</h1>
</div>

<div class="page-content">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">OpenSubtitles Configuration</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <form action="/admin/saveOpenSubtitlesSettings" method="post">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-control-label" for="api_key">API Key</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="api_key" name="api_key" 
                                   value="<%= opensubtitles_api_key %>" placeholder="Enter OpenSubtitles API Key">
                            <small class="form-text text-muted">
                                Get your API key from <a href="https://www.opensubtitles.com/en/consumers" target="_blank">OpenSubtitles API</a>
                            </small>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-control-label" for="username">Username</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" name="username" 
                                   value="<%= opensubtitles_username %>" placeholder="Enter OpenSubtitles Username">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-control-label" for="password">Password</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" 
                                   value="<%= opensubtitles_password %>" placeholder="Enter OpenSubtitles Password">
                            <small class="form-text text-muted">
                                Password will be stored securely and masked in the interface
                            </small>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Save Settings</button>
                            <a href="/admin" class="btn btn-default">Cancel</a>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="panel">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">About OpenSubtitles API</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>The OpenSubtitles API allows your application to search and download subtitles for movies and TV shows.</p>
                    
                    <h5>Setup Instructions:</h5>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Create an account at <a href="https://www.opensubtitles.com" target="_blank">OpenSubtitles.com</a></li>
                        <li>Apply for API access at the <a href="https://www.opensubtitles.com/en/consumers" target="_blank">developers page</a></li>
                        <li>Get your API key from your consumer dashboard</li>
                        <li>Enter your credentials above</li>
                    </ol>
                    
                    <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
                        <strong>Note:</strong> The API has rate limits. Make sure to follow their usage guidelines.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
